scraped_content.full_text: Portfolio Vishnu S I'm Machine Learning Enthusiast About I’m a passionate tech enthusiast with expertise in Machine Learning, Generative AI, and full-stack development. Constantly exploring innovative solutions, I thrive on building scalable applications and driving impactful projects. Passionate Curiosity-Driven Learner Birthday: 17 Sept 2003 Phone: +91 7397286386 City: Kangayem Age: 21 Degree: Bachelor Email: vishnusakthi.44@gmail.com LeetCode Questions Projects Completed Online Course CompletedNo of Hours Hackathon No of Attended Skills Eager Learning 100% JAVA 90% MongoDb 75% HTML & CSS 80% Python 90% Docker 55% < Resume Dynamic software engineer with hands-on experience in Machine Learning, Generative AI, and full-stack development. Passionate about crafting scalable solutions and driving impactful digital transformation projects. Summary Vishnu Motivated and enthusiastic Machine Learning graduate with a strong foundation in algorithms, data structures, and software development. Passionate about building intelligent systems and solving real-world problems using AI and ML techniques. Currently pursuing a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science Engineering with a focus on Machine Learning. Kongu Engineering College, Erode, Tamil Nadu, India vishnusakthi.44@gmail.com Education Bachelor of Technology in Computer Science Engineering (Machine Learning Specialization) 2022 - 2026 Kongu Engineering College, Erode, Tamil Nadu, India Currently pursuing a four-year degree with a focus on Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence, and Data Science. Gained hands-on experience with data analysis, ML algorithms, and Python programming. Projects Stock Price Prediction using Machine Learning 2023 Personal Project Developed a machine learning model to predict stock prices using historical data and machine learning techniques like Linear Regression and Decision Trees. Utilized Python libraries such as pandas, numpy, scikit-learn, and matplotlib for data processing, model building, and visualization. Implemented various performance evaluation metrics to assess the model's accuracy. Movie Recommendation System 2023 Personal Project Developed a movie recommendation system based on collaborative filtering using Python and machine learning techniques. Worked with datasets from MovieLens to recommend movies to users based on their preferences. Implemented both user-based and item-based recommendation algorithms. Skills Programming Languages: Python, Java, C++ Machine Learning Libraries: scikit-learn, TensorFlow, Keras, PyTorch Data Analysis: pandas, numpy, matplotlib, seaborn Database Management: MySQL, MongoDB Web Development: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React.js Version Control: Git, GitHub Projects Here are some of the projects that demonstrate my technical expertise and problem-solving abilities. Each project highlights my skills in various domains, from web development to machine learning and cloud deployment. Explore how I approach challenges and deliver innovative solutions.
